title: (Fri Full Show) Bailey Zimmerman Is With Us Talking About His New Album And Going Viral + Blind Karaoke: Country Love Songs + We Talk To Rita Wilson About Her New Music
itunes:title: (Fri Full Show) Bailey Zimmerman Is With Us Talking About His New Album And Going Viral + Blind Karaoke: Country Love Songs + We Talk To Rita Wilson About Her New Music
description:
Bailey Zimmerman calls into the studio to talk about what he hopes fans get from his debut album “Leave The Light On," how it feels going viral on Tik Tok and more! Plus, we play Blind Karaoke country love songs edition!  Hear us sing our version of these classic songs. Then, we get a sneak peek of Bobby's latest BobbyCast with Rita Wilson! She talks about her acting and music career, new music and more!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
